import React from 'react'
import FeatureBox from './FeatureBox'
import outil from '../images/outils.jpg'
import activites from '../images/activites.jpg'
import squelette from '../images/squelette.jpg'
import bwSchool from '../images/bwSchool.jpg'
import FeatureB from './FeatureB'

function Feature() {
  return (
    <section className='features'>
            <FeatureBox image={outil} texte="Nos Outils"/>
            <FeatureB image={activites} texte="Nos activites"/>
            <FeatureBox image={squelette} texte="Nos planches"/>
            <FeatureB image={bwSchool} texte="Nos loisirs"/>
    </section>
  )
}

export default Feature
